@startuml
title Agentic Flow v2.1.0 - Actual Run Flow

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

actor "Team Lead" as TL
participant "Product Manager" as PM
participant "Java Architect" as ARCH
participant "Reviewer" as REV
participant "Java Coder" as CODER

note over TL,CODER #E2E8F0
Green = passed gate
Yellow = rejected / returned
Red = red card
end note

group Planning Phase
TL -> PM : Create story
PM -[#22C55E]> TL : Story returned and accepted

TL -> ARCH : Create plan
ARCH -[#F59E0B]> TL : Plan returned\nwrong model picked;\nplan too large (~400 lines)
TL -[#22C55E]> TL : Plan accepted

TL -> REV : Phase 1 review
REV -[#22C55E]> TL : PASS
end

group Implementation Phase
TL -> CODER : Batch 1 (slices 1-2)
CODER --> TL : Handoff attempt
TL -[#F59E0B]> TL : Reject\nmissing implementation report\nand verification log

TL -> CODER : Batch 1 retry
CODER -[#22C55E]> TL : Valid batch 1 handoff

TL -> CODER : Batch 2 (slices 3-4)
CODER --> TL : Handoff attempt
TL -[#F59E0B]> TL : Reject\nmissing summary / no curl evidence

TL -> CODER : Batch 2 retry
CODER -[#22C55E]> TL : Summary returned
TL -[#22C55E]> TL : Build and tests accepted
end

group Review And Acceptance
TL -> REV : Phase 2 review
REV -[#F59E0B]> TL : PASS claimed\nwithout smoke evidence
TL -[#F59E0B]> TL : Reject reviewer result\nhandoff mismatch

TL -> REV : Reviewer rerun
REV -[#F59E0B]> TL : PASS claimed again\nstill no smoke evidence
TL -[#F59E0B]> TL : Reject reviewer result\nsmoke checks missing

TL -> REV : Reviewer rerun with curl verification
REV -[#22C55E]> TL : PASS with smoke evidence

TL -[#22C55E]> TL : Audit checks passed
TL -[#22C55E]> TL : Final sign-off
end

@enduml
